(2305, NULL, 'help.page.systemadministration', '<h3>System management</h3>\n<p>This page is to be used by the Cyberdam system manager. They can change system parameters, specify dialogue text in various languages, and inspect the logbook.</p>\n<p>Make your choice: parameters, language packs, logbook orSWF-directory.</p>', 1),
