(2324, NULL, 'help.page.playgroundimport', '<h3>Import playground</h3>\n<p>You can import a complete playground by pointing at the location of the corresponding zip-file and selecting &quot;Upload file&quot; subsequently. If the URI of the playground exists already, the system will ask you to change the it. After a successfull import, the system will display relevant statistics.</p>\n<p>Whenever an imported playground contains an SWF-file and the SWF directory of the Cyberdam system does not contain a n SWF file with that name, the SWF file will be incorporated into the Cyberdam system.</p>\n<p>After a successful import, the system displays some useful statistics. An imported playground automatically receives the status &quot;under construction&quot;. </p>', 1),
