(2355, NULL, 'help.page.groupadministration', '<h3>User group</h3>\n<p>A user group consists of:</p>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Category</b> - the type name of a user group, e.g. the name of an educational institute.</li>\n    <li><b>Group name</b> - the name of the users group.</li>\n    <li><b>Description </b>- a decription of the group.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>As soon as you have registered a group, you can make register and unregister users as a group member.</p>', 1),
