(2389, NULL, 'help.page.gamemodelactivities', '<h3>Activities</h3>\n<p>Through this page you can enter/edit the activities that are offered to a particular role during a particular step-of-play of the game. Cyberdam has the following types of activities:</p>\n<ul>\n    <li>Upload activity - an individual activity that leads to the uploading of a file,</li>\n    <li>Message activity - a social activity that ends in the sending of a message to a different role,&nbsp;</li>\n    <li>Form activity (v2.2) - an activity to fill in a form (input for the system)</li>\n    <li>Event activity (v2.3) - an activity to receive certain information (output from the system)</li>\n    <li>Progress activity - &nbsp;a progress activity that leads the game session to another step-of-play.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You add another activity by clicking the corresponding button. Then choose edit to give the activity a name or and/or specify its details.</p>', 1),
