(2397, NULL, 'help.page.languagepacks', '<h3>Language packs</h3>\n<p>This page contains an overview of the available language packages with dialogue texts. You can select a language package to add it.  A language package contains a number of dialogue texts. A dialogue text consists of a code (that is build into the software) and the text (in a certain language) that is shown on the screen of the user instead of that code. Dialogue texts can vary from single words without lay out to page long texts with distinctive lay out.</p>', 1),
