(2411, NULL, 'vleMessage.systemparam.comment', '<h3>Game session Notifications</h3> <p>During a game session the system may send e-mail notifications to the users. This can happen when a role receives a new message, or when the session as a whole moves to another step-of-play.&nbsp;Via their personal profile page  the users can set their preferences. The next two parameters set the default values of their preferences.</p>', 1),
(2412, NULL, 'help.page.gamemodelstepdetails', '<h3>More information needed?</h3> <p>Send an e-mail to <a href="mailto:helpdesk@cyberdam.nl">helpdesk@cyberdam.nl</a>&nbsp;referring to the title of your screen page and ask for it!</p>', 1),
