(2415, NULL, 'help.page.gamesessioncontrol', '<h3>Game session (control)</h3>\n<p>This page shows the current status of a game session (Running, Finished, Aborted) and the time the game session was started and perhaps stopped at. In the list of roles versus participants, you can edit the appointment of roles to participants if necessary. You can also view a game session from a certain role and even take over that role temporarily. If necessary you can abort the game session (no undo possible).</p>\n<p>Notice that several participants can play a certain role together. It is also possible that one participant plays several roles.</p>', 1),
