(2429, NULL, 'help.page.activities', '<h3>Activities</h3>\n<p>This page shows you the activities you can execute during the current step-of- play. When you choose a certain activity the following happens:&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n    <li>Upload activity - an individual activity that leads to the uploading of a file; upon completion, you will return to the session Home Page;</li>\n    <li>Message activity - a social activity that ends in the sending of a message to a different role;&nbsp; upon completion, you wil return to the session Home Page;</li>\n    <li>Form activity (v2.2) - an activity to fill in a form (input for the system); upon completion, you will return to the session Home Page;</li>\n    <li>Event activity (v2.3) - an activity to receive certain information (output from the system); upon completion, you will return to the session Home Page;</li>\n    <li>Progress activity - &nbsp;a progress activity that leads the game session to another step-of-play.</li>\n</ul>', 1),
