(2479, NULL, 'help.page.gameparticipant', '<h3>Game sessions</h3>\n<p>This table lists the game sessions you are participating in, i.e. in which you have been allocated to a certain role. Go to the home page of that session/role to proceed.</p>\n<p>Notice that it is possible that you play several roles in one game session; you then see that session several times in the list. It is also possible that you participate in several game sessions at the same time. If you do not see a game session at all, your game master might still be preparing it.</p>\n<p>The status of a game session is either:</p>\n<ul>\n    <li>Running - this is an active session; you may go to its home page to participate.</li>\n    <li>Finished - an active session that has come to its normal end; you may go to its home page to look at its end situation.</li>\n    <li>Aborted - an active session that has been forcefully ended by the game master; you may go to its home page to look at its situation on the moment it was forcefully ended.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1),
