(2597, NULL, 'help.page.useradministration', '<h3>Users</h3>\n<p>This page shows a list of registered users. You may hide all users that have not been activated. You may inspect or change the user details and delete a user record.</p>\n<p>Via this page you can add a new user. This can be done manually, on an individual base. It is also possible to do this automatically as a batch by uploading a file.</p>\n<h4>Uploading new users</h4>\n<p><span>In the case you want to register various users at the same time, you may save their data in a text file and upload that file. You will see immediately who has been registered as user before, who has been rejected and why. Please, print this information for future reference. It cannot be reproduced later.</span></p>\n<p><span>The text file is a so-called CSV file. Every user to be registered occupies a new line. Each line is built up from fields, separated by commas. Therefore, you should avoiud to use commas as part of your data. Do not use quotes either.</span></p>\n<p><span>A line consists of 15 fields in a fixed sequence:</span></p>\n<ol>\n    <li><span>First name</span></li>\n    <li><span>Last name </span></li>\n    <li><span>Login name</span>&nbsp;</li>\n    <li><span>Game (session) </span><span>Master (Nee = &quot;N&quot;, Ja = &quot;Y&quot;)</span></li>\n    <li><span>Game manifest composer (Nee = &quot;N&quot;, Ja = &quot;Y&quot;)</span></li>\n    <li><span>Game (model) author (Nee = &quot;N&quot;, Ja = &quot;Y&quot;)</span></li>\n    <li><span>Playground editor (Nee = &quot;N&quot;, Ja = &quot;Y&quot;)</span></li>\n    <li><span>LCMS-manager (Nee = &quot;N&quot;, Ja = &quot;Y&quot;)</span></li>\n    <li><span>LMS-manager (Nee = &quot;N&quot;, Ja = &quot;Y&quot;)</span></li>\n    <li><span>VLE-manager (Nee = &quot;N&quot;, Ja = &quot;Y&quot;)</span></li>\n    <li><span>Blanco veld,</span></li>\n    <li><span>Dialoue language (&quot;nl&quot; of &quot;en&quot;)</span></li>\n    <li><span>E-mail address</span></li>\n</ol>\n<h4><span>Sample&nbsp;upload.txt</span></h4>\n<p><code><span>Test, Game Master, testgm, Y, N, N, N, N, N, N, , nl, <a href="mailto:testgm@sofos.nl">testgm@cyberdam.nl</a><br />\nTest, Game Manifest Composer, testgmc, N, Y, N, N, N, N, N, , nl, <a href="mailto:testgmc@sofos.nl">testgmc@cyberdam.nl</a><br />\nTest, Game Author, testga, N, N, Y, N, N, N, N, , nl, <a href="mailto:testga@sofos.nl">testga@cyberdam.nl</a><br />\nTest, Playground Editor, testpe, N, N, N, Y, N, N, N, , nl, <a href="mailto:testpe@sofos.nl">testpe@cyberdam.nl</a><br />\nTest, LCMS Administrator, testlcms, N, N, N, N, Y, N, N, , nl, <a href="mailto:testlcms@sofos.nl">testlcms@cyberdam.nl</a><br />\nTest, LMS Administrator, testlms, N, N, N, N, N, Y, N, , nl, <a href="mailto:testlms@sofos.nl">testlms@cyberdam.nl</a><br />\nTest, VLE Administrator, testvle, N, N, N, N, N, N, Y, , nl, <a href="mailto:testvle@sofos.nl">testvle@cyberdam.nl</a></span></code></p>', 1),
