(2611, NULL, 'help.page.index', '<h3>Cyberdam Games</h3>\n<p><img alt="Cyberdam" src="http://www.cyberdam.nl/file.php/1/resources/images/flow0en.PNG" /></p>\n<h4>Explanation:</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Playground editors</b> can edit and extend playgrounds (map, objects, background information).</li>\n    <li><b>Game authors</b> can create or edit a game model (roles, steps-of-play, activities).</li>\n    <li><b>Game manifest composers</b> set the links between a game model and the playground; they associate a role in a game model with an object in a playground.</li>\n    <li><b>Game Masters</b> start and manage the game sessions. They allocate users to roles.</li>\n    <li><b>Participants</b> can play roles within game sessions; every registered user has this access and sees this entry.</li>\n    <li><b>User administration</b>; to register users and compile user groups.</li>\n    <li><b>Management</b>; to manage the Cyberdam system.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>Site-map</h4>\n<p>...</p>', 1),
