(2676, NULL, 'help.page.edituser', '<h3>User profile</h3>\n<p>The user profile consists of:</p>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>General data&nbsp;</b> - use a password with a length of six characters or more.</li>\n    <li><b>Rights </b>- these specify the privileges of a user.</li>\n    <li><b>Groups </b>- the user groups the user is a member of.</li>\n    <li><b>Preferences </b>- e.g. the dialogue language.</li>\n    <li><b>Statistieken</b> - the most recent login date and time.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you register a new user or changes their password, the system sends an automatic e-mail notification to them.</p>\n<p>Some changes become effective at the next time the user logs in.</p>', 1),
