(2784, NULL, 'uploadSizeMaxBytes.systemparam.comment', '<h3>Maximum file size</h3>\n<p>When uploading files, a maximum file size applies. This has to be specified in two different locations:</p>\n<ol>\n    <li>The system manager sets the maximum upload file size in the fiel WEB-INF/dispatcher-servlet.xml in the Cyberdam war. This XML file contains a definition with id multipartResolver with maxUploadSize in bytes inside. Default value 5242880. After editing, tomcat has to be restarted.</li>\n    <li>The application manager sets the maximum value via the system oarameters page (see next line). Its value may not exceed the value set by the system manager.</li>\n</ol>', 1),
