(2814, NULL, 'help.page.gamemodelgameplay', '<h3>Activities schedule</h3>\n<p>This page shows a matrix of roles and steps-of-play; in every cell&nbsp; 0, 1 or more activities can be found, that will be offered to that particular role during that particular step-of-play.</p>\n<p>In every cell of the matrix you can choose adding of activities. You can also choose to delete added activities. If you wish to add a role or step-of-play or the list of available activities you can do so through other pages. Finally you can indicate at which step-of-play a game session should start; normally this will be the first step-of-play. The game session ends as soon as a step-of-play is achieved in which none of the roles is offered any activity whatsoever.</p>', 1),
