(2845, NULL, 'help.page.printablesessionreport', '<h3>Report: standard report game session</h3>\n<p>This document contains the standard report of a Cuyberdam game session. The contents partially depends on the date and time the report is created. The report lists the playgrounds used, the game model, the game manifest and the game session itself.&nbsp;It displays all roles and the names of the users allocated to them at the time the report was generated. The report concludes with the session logbook, a chronological list&nbsp;of all important events during the game session.&nbsp;Cyberdam is a product of Stichting RechtenOnline (<a href="http://www.cyberdam.nl">http://www.cyberdam.nl</a>).</p>', 1),
