(2897, NULL, 'help.page.gameauthor', '<h3>Game models</h3>\n<p>Game authors can create or edit a game model. Here they set certain activities that roles can develop during particular steps-of-play. This page contains a list of game models. You can view, edit, delete and copy existing game models. You can also add a new game model. If you give a game model the status of &quot;Personal&quot;, you can include it in a game manifest and have game sessions. As long as they are active you can view and copy the game model, but not edit it. You can also give your game model the status &ldquo;Public&rdquo;. In that case you hand it over to the publisher who distributes it to third parties and lets them use it under certain conditions.</p>', 1),
