(2935, NULL, 'help.page.multilanguage', '<h3>Language pack</h3>\n<p>This page shows the list of dialogue texts the selected language package is built of. A dialogue text consists of a code (that is build into the software) and the text (in the selected language) that is shown on the screen of the user instead of that code. You can edit or delete these texts. You can also add a new dialogue text.</p>', 1),
